</div>

















<div id="paragraph-AeTV0YVZsR3JvcXI2O__paragraph_DaCh4x" class="body-text [&_a]:underline font-primary text-sm md:text-xs text-ink-secondary font-normal leading-normal tracking-normal  text-left md:text-left w-full md:w-full" style="" >
  
  
    <div><p>We are an independent family owned jewellers since 1990, with stores in Coventry and Loughborough. We offer in-house bespoke jewellery design and making service through the expertise of our on-site Gemmologist's and Goldsmith's, valuations, watch and jewellery repairs, watch and jewellery cleaning, insurance replacements and bracelet alterations.<br/><br/>We are proud to be able to offer you some of the most sort after fashion, designer and luxury brands including: <a href="/pages/explore-bell-ross" title="Explore Bell & Ross">Bell & Ross</a>, <a href="/collections/gucci" title="Gucci">Gucci</a>, <a href="/pages/explore-grand-seiko" title="Explore Grand Seiko">Grand Seiko</a>, <a href="/pages/explore-hamilton" title="Explore Hamilton">Hamilton</a>, <a href="/pages/explore-longines" title="Explore Longines">Longines</a>, <a href="/pages/explore-oris" title="Explore Oris">Oris</a>, <a href="/pages/explore-rado" title="Explore Rado">RADO</a>, <a href="/pages/explore-tag-heuer" title="Explore TAG Heuer">TAG Heuer</a>, <a href="/collections/swarovski" title="Swarovski">Swarovski </a>and many more. We are an official UK jewellers, so you can be assured of receiving the genuine article with the manufacturer backed warranty.<br/><br/>Shop online with confidence, we offer numerous safe and secure payment options including PayPal, Amazon Pay, Apple Pay, Google Pay, Klarna and more. Free UK delivery (orders over £75.00), 30 day returns (T&C's apply), same day dispatch (order by 3:00pm Mon-Fri) and the same great service we offer in store.<br/><br/>If you would like to speak to us, please call us on 0800 977 4391 (+44 800 977 4391 International) during working hours, or email sales@francisandgaye.co.uk, a member of our friendly and knowledgeable team will be happy to assist you.</p></div>
  

</div>




  <style data-shopify>
